{"id":220572,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/04/global-voices-地球一日：全球合作的音乐影片推出/","date":"2012-04-13T08:34:30Z","modified":"2012-04-13T08:34:30Z","title":"Global Voices | 地球一日：全球合作的音乐影片推出","content":"<p><p>为了宣传”地球一日(One Day on Earth)”这部全球合作的电影，推出了一支<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://vimeo.com/39875998\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/39875998\">新的音乐影片</a>，该片将于地球日(2012年4月22日)在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/02/22/one-day-on-earth-global-screening-of-pioneer-worldwide-collaborative-film/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/02/22/one-day-on-earth-global-screening-of-pioneer-worldwide-collaborative-film/\">全球同步上映</a>。影片全部在2010年10月10日的24小时内拍摄，捕捉音乐家、诗人和舞者们的演出，再由Cut Chemist巧妙地剪辑和混音。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.onedayonearth.org/\" href=\"http://www.onedayonearth.org/\">地球一日</a>这部全球携手合作的影片，全部都在2010年10月10日同一天拍摄完成，从世界各地传来总计超过3000小时的连续镜头，呈现在一天内所发生的令人赞叹的多样性、冲突、悲剧和欢欣。经由世界遗址和联合国的协助，将在地球日(2012年4月22日)这天在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.onedayonearth.org/screening\" href=\"http://www.onedayonearth.org/screening\">全球各国上映</a>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>音乐影片包含从印度、巴布亚新几内亚、贝南、布吉纳法索、美国、中国、北韩、蒙古、肯尼亚、阿富汗、雅买加、西班牙、台湾以及很多其他地方的镜头。</p>\n<p>更多上映相关的讯息，可阅读我们前一篇文章<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/02/22/one-day-on-earth-global-screening-of-pioneer-worldwide-collaborative-film/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/02/22/one-day-on-earth-global-screening-of-pioneer-worldwide-collaborative-film/\">地球一日: 世界共同合作电影将作全球联映</a>，也可在<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.onedayonearth.org/screening\" href=\"http://www.onedayonearth.org/screening\">One Day on Earth</a>网站登入，要求在你的所在城镇放映此片。</p>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F13%2F10803%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F13%2F10803%2F&#038;desc=%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F13%2F10803%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F13%2F10803%2F&#038;text=%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F13%2F10803%2F&#038;title=%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA\" title=\"reddit\"><span>reddit</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.stumbleupon.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F13%2F10803%2F&#038;title=%E5%9C%B0%E7%90%83%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA\" title=\"StumbleUpon\"><span>StumbleUpon</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://del.icio.us/post?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F04%2F13%2F10803%2F&#038;title=%E